column1: Baby Barnaby's////I ordered the green eggs
column2: and everyone who's had them was right. It is delicious. It also comes with little hash browns
column4: and toast. I honestly think the dish is fine without the sausage because the eggs have enough flavor by itself. I feel like the apple sausage overpowers the green eggs. What I liked about the eggs
column5: was that it was not too rich. It also had a nice garlicky
